Here is some event in form.
    submit: 
            1. submit
    
    input: 
            1. keydown
            2. keyup
            3. keypress
            4. focus
            5. blur
            6. cut
            7. paste
            8. copy


    EXAMPLE SUBMIT:
        <form (submit)="onSubmit($event)"></form>

    EXAMPLE INPUT:
        <input (keydown)="fireEvent($event)" type=text name="someName"></form>